N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 205.7 - Research

State Regulations

The commissioner is hereby authorized to contract with, upon the advice of the advisory board, any person or persons, such as the

Cornell University College of Agriculture and Life Sciences, to carry on or
cause to be carried on cabbage production, harvesting, storage, and marketing
quality research, and to expend any available monies for such purpose and
pursuant to this order. Notes
